User Log

Version:MissionOS_2.0

User Log page is a display of the user's login history into the MissionOS portal with details like User's name, IP address, Modified Time, Action, Original, Changed, Recalculation if any.

The number of entries shown can be changed to 10, 25, 50 and 100.

You can use the Search functionality to search for any of the user’s login information you require from this page.
